Drew Catherine (Party Woman). Tricia Black (Data-Act Protester). Sabrina Saudin (Ristorante Waitress). Jamaal Ellis (416. Protest Crowd #3). Ferelith Young (Woman). Mark Winnick (Young Crowley).
